---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Blog"
  description="Learn more about our company, team, and mission."
  image="/images/blog/about-og.jpg"
  current="blog"
  additionalStyles=""
>
  <Fragment slot="headContent">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/blog_inner.css" />
  </Fragment>

  <div class="site-header">
    <div class="container1 scale-item">
      <h1>
        Revolutionizing Digital Experiences: How 3D Animation, AR and VR Are
        Transforming Industries
      </h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="container1">
    <img
      src="/images/blog/3d-ar-vr-transforming-industries.jpg"
      alt="AR VR Digital Experiences by Fisto"
      class="animate-item from-bottom"
    />

    <section id="why-ar-vr" class="animate-item from-bottom">
      <h2>Why Businesses Need AR, VR and 3D Animation in 2025 and Beyond</h2>
      <p>
        Today, consumers crave engaging, interactive content and technologies
        like 3D animation, Augmented Reality (AR), and Virtual Reality (VR) are
        meeting that demand head-on. Consumer Expectations Have Changed.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="fisto-solutions" class="animate-item from-bottom">
      <h2>Fisto’s Cutting-Edge Solutions That Set It Apart</h2>
      <p>
        At Fisto, we use the latest technology to make AR, VR, and 3D content.
        Our work helps brands stand out, explain ideas clearly, and connect with
        people.
      </p>

      <h3>3D Animation That Brings Your Brand to Life</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>We create realistic 3D models to show off products clearly.</li>
        <li>
          We make animated videos to explain things in education, healthcare,
          and marketing.
        </li>
        <li>
          We design eye-catching content for events, presentations, and product
          launches.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3>AR Development for Retail & Engagement</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Customers can see and try products before buying.</li>
        <li>Fun AR campaigns that get people interested and involved</li>
      </ul>
    </section>


    <img
      src="/images/blog/blog1_img2.webp"
      alt="AR VR Digital Experiences by Fisto"
      class="animate-item from-bottom"
    />
    <section id="future-trends" class="animate-item from-bottom">
      <h2>Future Trends in AR, VR, and 3D Animation</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>AI will help make 3D designs faster and easier.</li>
        <li>
          VR will feel more real by using not just sight and sound, but also
          touch.
        </li>
        <li>
          AR will work directly on websites, so no need to download an app.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div id="faq" class="animate-item from-bottom">
        <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

        <div class="card1">
          <h4>
            <strong
              >1.What sectors are most impacted by AR/VR and 3D animation?</strong>
          </h4>
          <p>
            Key sectors like manufacturing, healthcare, education, real estate,
            and retail use immersive tech to connect with customers and upskill
            employees through engaging, virtual environments.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card1">
          <h4><strong>2.What’s the difference between AR and VR?</strong></h4>
          <p>
            AR: computer-generated images and information onto the real world,
            typically viewed through the screen of a smartphone, tablet, or AR
            headset. <br />
            VR:VR immerses the user in a completely computer-generated environment,
            blocking out the real world.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card1">
          <h4>
            <strong
              >3.Can Fisto integrate AR/VR into my mobile app or website?</strong>
          </h4>
          <p>
            Yes! Fisto can add AR/VR to your app or site for better user
            experience and engagement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="conclusion" class="animate-item from-bottom">
      <h2>Conclusion</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Shape the Future of Engagement with Fisto:</strong> We help brands
        connect through interactive 3D and AR/VR. Let your audience explore your
        story—virtually.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
